572
00:31:57,603 --> 00:31:58,822
Je suis Liz Oxenberg.

573
00:32:00,231 --> 00:32:01,233
Oxenberg.

574
00:32:01,611 --> 00:32:03,586
Oui, elle-même.

575
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,710
- Bonjour.
- Voici Max.

576
00:32:14,278 --> 00:32:15,809
- Salut, Max.
- Bonjour.

577
00:32:17,199 --> 00:32:18,978
